        "Name": "SF: Ultimate Promotion Exam",
        "Client": "Karate Man in Pink",
        "Description": "Looking to train with the best,\r\nI see! Well, you came to the\r\nright place! My prized pupil\r\nis\u2014Hold on, there\u0027s two of\r\n\u0027em!? And the second one has\r\na dark aura!? *shrug* Anyway,\r\nyou just need to defeat one!",
